    h2.section__title Business case
    p WP Engine has prioritized and cultivated an Agency Partner Program in an effort to support a massive customer base with exponential revenue growth attached to it. This documentary caters to that audience, tells their story, and celebrates their contribution to ---the internet revolution ---how the internet affects society.

    p The make|SHIFT documentary focuses on a portion of that community, the creators who worked with large brands in the early days of the internet to figure out how to use a new technology to reach new audiences, new consumers.  It tells the story of how we went from banner ads and popups to magically interactive experiences like Burger King's Subservient Chicken.

